# Basic usage

    |---------+-------------------------------|
    | C-x C-s | Save                          |
    | C-x C-f | Load/open                     |
    | C-s     | Isearch forward               |
    | C-r     | Isearch backwards             |
    | C-:     | Eval (useful for conig stuff) |
    |---------+-------------------------------|

#  Buffers

    |---------+-----------------------|
    | C-x C-e | Run command in buffer |
    | C-x o   | Move to next buffer   |
    | C-x b   | Select a buffer       |
    |---------+-----------------------|

# Shell

    |---------+----------------------------------------------|
    | M-!     | Execute shell command - output in new buffer |
    | C-u M-! | Insert shell output at point                 |
    |---------+----------------------------------------------|

# Other stuff

    |---------------------------+--------------------|
    | M-x eshell                | Open a shell       |
    | M-x eshell                | Open a shell       |
    | M-x goto-line             | Goto a line number |
    | M-x toggle-word-wrap      | Word wrap          |
    | M-x flyspell-mode         | Spell checking     |
    | M-x linum-mode            | Line numbers       |
    | M-x visual-line-mode      | Toggle line wrap   |
    | M-x compile               | Compile some code  |
    | M-x package-list-packages | List packages      |
    |---------------------------+--------------------|

#  Sudoing within eshell

  By default when using the sudo command within eshell you'll just
  get "permission denied" messages. To overcome that type:

    alias sudo '*sudo $*'

# Org-mode

    |----------------+--------------------------------------------|
    | M-x org-mode   | To begin org-mode                          |
    | Vertical-pipe  | Table column separator                     |
    | TAB            | Reorganize table                           |
    | *              | Section heading                            |
    | TAB            | Open/collapse section                      |
    | C-TAB          | Open/collapse All                          |
    | C-c C-e        | Export in other file formats (eg HTML,PDF) |
    | C-c pipe       | Convert selection into table!!!            |
    | M-<up/down>    | Move row up/down                           |
    | M-<left/right> | Move column left/right!                    |
    | C-c ^          | Sort table based on culumn under point     |
    |----------------+--------------------------------------------|
    
## Org lists

    |----------------+-------------------------------------------------------|
    | M-RET          | Add new todo item/checkbox                            |
    | M-<right/left> | Change subdivision of item                            |
    | M-<up/down>    | Move item up/down along with all subitems             |
    | S-<left/right> | Toggle todo-item                                      |
    | - [ ]          | Start a checkbox entry                                |
    | C-c C-c        | Toggle checkbox                                       |
    | [/] -- C-c C-c | Display the num items completed on parent (aka [2/3]) |
    | [%] -- C-c C-c | Display pourcentage completed on parent (aka [66%])   |
    | C-c C-d        | Popup calendars and pick a deadline for item          |
    |----------------+-------------------------------------------------------|

# Finding stuff

    |-------+----------------------------------------|
    | C-h m | All info + bindings about current mode |
    | C-h f | Get info about a Emacs Lisp function   |
    | C-h v | Get info about a variable              |
    |-------+----------------------------------------|
